QuestData.Title: Back to the Lab
QuestData.Description:
Our work here is done!
Well, at least until another one of my humble experiments goes horribly awry, rapidly spiraling out of control into a chain reaction of catastrophic failures.
But, let's worry about that another time, $p.
I'll meet you back at my lab!
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Raimond Mildenhall in his Raimond's Laboratory.
QuestData.RewardText:
Well, we had quite the adventure $p.
Let's try not to do that again anytime soon though!
